race.comment: BLAINE KEEPING (1) goes very well this course and distance starting 16 times for nine wins and four minors. Hit the frame latest (18.22) when second at this track in a NG. Rates on top and should go close. COCO MAC (7) was in the placings last time but prior to that clocked a solid 19.65 win over 340m at Gunnedah. Should be in this for a long way. HOW FAST (2) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten third (19.03) in a Grade 5 at Temora last time out. Can feature with the right run. AMAZING GEM (5) has a solid strike rate at this distance.
